==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|entretenir}}, from {{m|fro|entre||among}} + {{m|fro|tenir||to hold}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|inter}} + {{m|la|teneō||hold, keep}}. For the noun, compare French {{m|fr|entretien}}.

